###Instruction:WriteacompletePythonscripttosolvetheKaggleTitaniccompetition.Usepandasfordataloading,scikit-learnforaRandomForestClassifier,handlemissingvalues,andsavepredictionsto'submission.csv'.Inputfilesare'train.csv'and'test.csv'.###Response:ƒäƒäHereƒ†isƒ†aƒ†Pythonƒ†scriptƒ†thatƒ†solvesƒ†theƒ†Kaggleƒ†Titanicƒ†competitionƒ†usingƒ†pandasƒ†forƒ†dataƒ†loading,ƒ†scikit-learnƒ†forƒ†aƒ†Randomƒ†Forestƒ†Classifier,ƒ†handlesƒ†missingƒ†values,ƒ†andƒ†savesƒ†theƒ†predictionsƒ†toƒ†aƒ†submission.csvƒ†file.ƒäƒä```pythonƒäimportƒ†pandasƒ†asƒ†pdƒäfromƒ†sklearn.ensembleƒ†importƒ†RandomForestClassifierƒäfromƒ†sklearn.imputeƒ†importƒ†SimpleImputerƒäƒä#ƒ†Loadƒ†dataƒätrain_dataƒ†=ƒ†pd.read_csv('train.csv')ƒätest_dataƒ†=ƒ†pd.read_csv('test.csv')ƒäƒä#ƒ†Handleƒ†missingƒ†valuesƒäimputerƒ†=ƒ†SimpleImputer(strategy='mean')ƒätrain_dataƒ†=ƒ†imputer.fit_transform(train_data)ƒätest_dataƒ†=ƒ†imputer.transform(test_data)ƒäƒä#ƒ†Defineƒ†featuresƒ†andƒ†targetƒäfeaturesƒ†=ƒ†train_data.drop(['Survived'],ƒ†axis=1)ƒätargetƒ†=ƒ†train_data['Survived']ƒäƒä#ƒ†Defineƒ†theƒ†Randomƒ†Forestƒ†Classifierƒäclfƒ†=ƒ†RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=100,ƒ†random_state=0)ƒäƒä#ƒ†Fitƒ†theƒ†modelƒäclf.fit(features,ƒ†target)ƒäƒä#ƒ†Makeƒ†predictionsƒäpredictionsƒ†=ƒ†clf.predict(test_data)ƒäƒä#ƒ†Createƒ†aƒ†submissionƒ†dataframeƒäsubmissionƒ†=ƒ†pd.DataFrame({ƒäƒ†ƒ†ƒ†ƒ†'PassengerId':ƒ†test_data['PassengerId'],ƒäƒ†ƒ†ƒ†ƒ†'Survived':ƒ†predictionsƒä})ƒäƒä#ƒ†Saveƒ†theƒ†submissionƒ†dataframeƒ†toƒ†aƒ†csvƒ†fileƒäsubmission.to_csv('submission.csv',ƒ†index=False)ƒä```ƒäƒäThisƒ†scriptƒ†firstƒ†loadsƒ†theƒ†trainingƒ†andƒ†testingƒ†data,ƒ†thenƒ†itƒ†imputesƒ†missingƒ†valuesƒ†inƒ†theƒ†trainingƒ†dataƒ†usingƒ†theƒ†meanƒ†strategy.ƒ†Itƒ†thenƒ†definesƒ†theƒ†featuresƒ†andƒ†theƒ†targetƒ†forƒ†theƒ†Randomƒ†Forestƒ†Classifier,ƒ†fitsƒ†theƒ†model,ƒ†makesƒ†predictions,ƒ†andƒ†createsƒ†aƒ†submissionƒ†dataframe.ƒ†Finally,ƒ†itƒ†savesƒ†theƒ†submissionƒ†dataframeƒ†toƒ†aƒ†csvƒ†file.ƒä